 0px; widows: 2; orphans: 2; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: ''times new roman serif'';">6.</span><span style="font-family: ''仿宋_gb2312 serif'';">退化性视网膜黄斑部区病变者</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; widows: 2; orphans: 2; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: ''times new roman serif'';">7.</span><span style="font-family: ''仿宋_gb2312 serif'';">接受过近视雷射者</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; widows: 2; orphans: 2; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: ''times new roman serif'';">8.</span><span style="font-family: ''仿宋_gb2312 serif'';">肾功能退化导致视网膜退化患者</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; widows: 2; orphans: 2; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: ''仿宋_gb2312 serif'';">【关于叶黄素】</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; widows: 2; orphans: 2; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: ''仿宋_gb2312 serif'';">叶黄素是在眼睛视网膜和晶状体被发现的类胡萝卜素，对我们的眼睛非常重要。研究表明叶黄素对眼睛的主要生理功能是作为抗氧化剂和光保护作用。国内外研究发现人类视网膜中叶黄素浓度与视觉敏感度和老年性视网膜黄斑变性的发生有关。摄取叶黄素含量高的食物，有助于降低、延缓眼睛的老化、退化、病变，减少眼疾的发生率，还可以保护视网膜免受光线的伤害。同时研究还表明叶黄素具有抗氧化性，能防止大肠癌等肿瘤病变以及血管硬化。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; widows: 2; orphans: 2; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">本品由具有</span><span style="font-family: ''calibri sans-serif'';">50</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">多年历史的加拿大一流大厂</span><span style="font-family: ''calibri sans-serif'';">WEBBER NATURALS</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">生产</span><span style="font-family: ''calibri sans-serif'';">,</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">出自工厂自己的有机农场！</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; widows: 2; orphans: 2; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); backgro